is_prime(N) :-
    N > 1,
    \+ ( between(2, N-1, X),
         N mod X =:= 0 ).

Explanation

N > 1 â†’ prime numbers start from 2

between(2, N-1, X) â†’ checks all numbers between 2 and Nâˆ’1

N mod X =:= 0 â†’ checks divisibility

